World "LogicWorld1"
Title "Logic Part 1"

Introduction
"
We start our journey by introducing two elementary statement types:
**existence** statements and **conjunctions**.

For each type `T` we discuss two tactics. One of them allows us
to construct a proof for `T` while the other enables us to use
information hidden in a hypothesis of type `T`.
"
